nodes.title: Complete AI Screenplay Video Generation (Robust)
widgets_values:
ROBUST END-TO-END SYSTEM:

1. ✅ FIXED: ImageScale nodes for reliable image standardization (512×512)
2. ✅ FIXED: Native ImageBatch for robust image batching
3. ✅ FIXED: GetBatchSize (kjnodes) for reliable counting
4. ✅ AI generates screenplay prompts using proper shrug-prompter architecture
5. ✅ Prompts feed into WAN VACE processing loop for actual video generation
6. ✅ Final output: MP4 video file with VHS_VideoCombine

Robust improvements:
✅ Native ComfyUI nodes (more stable)
✅ Standardized 512×512 images (better VLM processing)
✅ kjnodes GetBatchSize (purpose-built for counting)
✅ Eliminated ImpactMakeImageBatch compatibility issues
A character's journey from isolation to connection
